title: Milestone 1.11 -  Gather Project Details (Time to PO: 104 to 78 Weeks)
description:
Milestone - 1.11: Gather Project Details (Time to PO: 104 to 78 Weeks)

-       Owner: PSE Labs Readiness Lead

-       Start: 104 weeks before PO

-       Complete: 78 weeks before PO

Overview:

Early readiness planning steps - product timeline,identifying the labs, and adding the project name to HSD.  Document the needs and progress in the ticketcomments.

#

Action

Notes / Examples / Visual Aids

1        

Give product timeline and detailed input

Collect the information about the project including Prognos loaded correctly (Quanity, functions, sites and type of systems), OPL and Atlas and check PO dates are correct.

2        

Define locations based on site infrastructure capacity

Work with partners and agree on the distribution of systems across the labs.  Determine what the current state of lab capacity is based on the PSE LIT.

3        

Update HSD-ES with the project name

Create HSD-ES project name using Prognos official project name.
